dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\"}, {\"begin\": 686, \"end\": 693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.714834698832526, \"rank\": 0.3676842089275147, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 704, \"end\": 709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.923117033065196e-21, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her victory also marked China's second tennis gold in the history of the Games after Li Na and Sun Tiantian won the women's doubles title in Athens in 2004.\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 943, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 811, \"end\": 816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9031202693670249, \"rank\": 0.10724987981377777, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 872, \"end\": 877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Li_Na\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.02516827356049e-40, \"text\": \"Li Na\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Li_Na\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Li_Na\"}, {\"begin\": 882, \"end\": 894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Tiantian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sun Tiantian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Tiantian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Tiantian\"}, {\"begin\": 928, \"end\": 934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.451098056466771e-18, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Right now I feel super excited,\\\" Zheng said after the final.\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 1006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 979, \"end\": 984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.872404112985476e-18, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Because before the Olympic Games, I have not thought I got to win the gold medal.\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1089, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I always have expectations since 2022 for this Olympic Games, but the moment I won this gold medal, nothing can describe this feeling because I have been working so hard for this moment, representing the country.\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1302, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I am so happy to become the first one and make the history for China.\\\"\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1370, \"end\": 1375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9031202693670249, \"rank\": 0.10724987981377777, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Li Na inspired me a lot when I was a child,\\\" Zheng added.\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1425, \"end\": 1430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.872404112985476e-18, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She put the dream seed inside me when she won her first Grand Slams, when she broke the records for Asian girls in tennis.\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1539, \"end\": 1544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.923117033065196e-21, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Right now, here I am.\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am really happy to become the first one to win the Olympic medal for China in tennis.\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1671, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1655, \"end\": 1660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9031202693670249, \"rank\": 0.10724987981377777, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I hope that my achievement can inspire more young kids, make them love tennis, because I always feel tennis is such a great sport.\\\"\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1807, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"L-R: Silver medalist Sun Yingsha and gold medalist Chen Meng of China and bronze medalist Hina Hayata of Japan pose for a photo after the women's singles table tennis final at the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris, France, August 3, 2024.\", \"from\": 1809, \"to\": 2043, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1830, \"end\": 1841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Yingsha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sun Yingsha\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13382519\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia